Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖畔的夢幻少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了\N行才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的詭計早就被我們看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你的目的一定是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有工作的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我去做些自己喜歡的事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們難道不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最討厭去沒有女人的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繼續走吧 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特他真是的 還是那副蠢相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為什麼會那麼的好色呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神 可不可以告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 看著他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心裡就會很平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到達目的地了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那地方滿漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是早上的時候 風景特別漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特就只知道泡妞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望他偶爾也能打開心胸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛愛這片大自然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女人 衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那邊去就只有湖而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.59,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他 別管他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他大概還在做白日夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了湖邊他就會清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 是個孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…還真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔…叔叔?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒到被叫叔叔的地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給妳當作交往的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我還只是個小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不分年齡的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說妳叫蕾克?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凱洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特葛拉瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蕾克妳有沒有姊姊呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳媽媽幾歲?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孤苦伶仃一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了? 凱洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起玩好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去叼回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪 汪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖 凱洛特哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣拿著…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快追上來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓到妳了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對 我要那個藍色的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點點就弄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好開心哦 凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次好像可以期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想要請妳答應我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我答應你?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妳長大了再跟我一起玩好不好?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在打壞主意對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和我一起玩 其實也是為了那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特葛拉瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將是這世界這次的代表者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛看起來沒精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見他真的很想在這地方追個女孩子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我就來讓他振奮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那個閒工夫的話就來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在馬龍把食物買回來之前我想先準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下再讓他高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來好像很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這副德性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當作交往的信物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那個叫做蕾克的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得很像是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長相是不像啦 可是味道很像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是妳長得比較漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該向你說聲謝謝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓凱洛特先生來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 還沒問妳名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到你把我變成女人之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再…告…訴…你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人家這麼擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你又跟女孩子鬼魂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩子怎麼不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 只要一有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就動歪腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 真的很奇怪耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說 在這種深山湖邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有年輕女孩呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬龍你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼找個吃的東西找這麼久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了 趕快離開這裡 這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:11:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽附近村子的人說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天早上以前 靠近湖邊會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好誘人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下等一下 這位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不想跟姊姊快樂一下啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是蕾克…對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚的那個女孩也是妳 對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳是用這種方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,履行兒時的諾言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會看得出來?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經改變了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣啊 完全沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.97,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我曾經喜歡過的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管她變成什麼樣子我都認得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事自開世以來還是頭一遭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就老實告訴你吧 凱洛特葛拉瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這個湖…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠在人類誕生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直看著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且每一百年就判斷一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是否適合這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累積了百年的湖水能量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我們這些湖水精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻化成人形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就是那個精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是用那種方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來判定人心的善惡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈所遇到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成了代表者而被試探
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人如果心地不好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湖水就會化為濁流氾濫各個村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那凱洛特應該不會怎麼樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他有時會打些壞主意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是心地不好的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都會沒命的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了一百年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會等到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在湖外…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能待很短的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見面得時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定是老太婆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該是離別的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作交往的信物好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這孩子一點兒都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不過是昨天才發生的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻恍如隔世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是她嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是湖水精靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 等一下她就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著我這樣的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒什麼好高興的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 美麗的女人是不分年齡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是短時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻是和你渡過了幸福的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事想要拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要拜託我?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳願不願意再陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在打什麼壞主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想這樣子跟我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了那個目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的絕對不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該是離開的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝你 凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要讓我變成女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再一起玩哦 凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個情況 他沒有變成犧牲品的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的 我也希望能夠一直 一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪著凱洛特到他老
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他這人好色得無藥可救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀?\N慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個史普露那大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會施法術的魔法師們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以法力支配人們 統治天下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為統治手段極為殘暴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無力抵抗的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能過著以淚洗面的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 對這些民眾而言 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還有一線希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是這裡有一群替天行道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專門懲治殘暴魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來去無蹤的正義戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們都稱他們為爆走獵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊好漂亮哦 趕快看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我是多塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們覺得凱洛特和馬龍之間是不是感情很好?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是馬龍他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他老說大哥真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得那是他對大哥愛的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕 他們兄弟之間的感情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好他們倆是兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們是兄妹的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會轉變成畸戀的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 將會是如何呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆走獵人第六集 極端的水晶之愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要振作一點 大哥

